{"title":"拾棉花","authors":["钟铃"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":10,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"拾棉花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钟铃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青青的棵子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪绒绒的花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新娶的媳妇拾棉花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花桃结的一挂挂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胖胖的手儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摘一朵，揪一下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回过头来看看他："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你瞧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这花开的有多大？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他年青，个子大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这块棉花地由他养种大："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“花儿开的大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是咱劳动下；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天家里少个你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"互助点种靠大家！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"媳妇听了微微笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小伙子紧紧又拾两把，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他问她："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你可会务庄稼？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“咱土生土长这么大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从小就在地里爬……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她昂起头来看一下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滴溜溜的黑眼珠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看的小伙子羞答答。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胖胖的脸儿红光光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说罢两人低头想——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土改分了地和房，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了吃也有了穿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"组织起来闹生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄户人要报答咱新国家！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摘了一朵又一朵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你一把来我一把，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小俩口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一包一包，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摘到太阳下。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}